To sum view cells: view of i32, giving i32.
Let total be 0.
For each index i of cells: total becomes total plus cells at i.
Give total.

To nested owned view, giving i32.
Let total be 0.
For i from 0 up to 3: Let cells be owned buffer of 2 i32 filled with i; total becomes total plus sum view cells.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Give nested owned view.
